\h COLOSSENSES
\toc1 Paulo Liwakatetigi Colosseenitedi
\toc2 Colossenses
\toc3 Cl
\mt1 PAULO LIWAKATETIGI COLOSSEENSITEDI
\ip NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide aca nigotaЙЎМ¶a Colossos iteloco nipodigi ГЃsia, analeeЙЎМ¶oyatigi me nipodigi Turquia niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi. Paulo aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a dalita naЙЎМ¶ajo nigotaЙЎМ¶a, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica lapo loiigi Cristo anidiaa liЙЎМ¶eladi. Paulo idei niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi naЙЎМ¶a idГ­ naЙЎМ¶adi liwakate.
\ip Paulo owidi ane iditeloco naЙЎМ¶adi liwakate niЙЎМ¶inoa anijo maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iditibige Efeesiotedi. NiЙЎМ¶ina me yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, diniotagodetalo leeЙЎМ¶odi lewiЙЎМ¶a Colosseensitedi. Paulo eledi diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece З¤oniotagodi Jesus me niЙЎМ¶ijaa lacilo loiigi, idiaaЙЎМ¶idi micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a lolaadi anowidi liwailidi. Paulo eo leemidi leeЙЎМ¶odi niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco ane deЙЎМ¶ewiteda. YalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ijo oxiiЙЎМ¶odi anejinaЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a, codaa eledi yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ida gela anejinaЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶odexogotege Cristo. Paulo iladee wadonadi, eniododipi inaa nionigipi, niotagipi inaa otagododi, yeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi anodaa leeditibige me ee lewiЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi monakato З¤oniotagodi.
\c 1
\s1 Paulo yecoaditibige Colosseensitedi
\p 
\v 1-2 Ee Paulo, ee liiЙЎМ¶exegi Jesus Cristo, igaataЙЎМ¶a joaniЙЎМ¶idaa ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibakedi. З¤onioxoa TimГіteo ini meetaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶a jiwakateetibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi anakaami liomaЙЎМ¶ataka AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, anakaami niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Colossos, anakaami ЙЎМ¶onioxoadipi ane ЙЎМ¶adexocitege Cristo, codaa anidioka limedi me iwitece liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco.
\p JipokaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iniaa З¤oniotagodi Jesus Cristo mowo aneletaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji, codaa mowo ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali mele.
\s1 Paulo yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji codaa me diniotagodetalo
\p 
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶ina me jotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, jipokaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶alocotiwaji, codaa midioka limedi me iniotagodeeЙЎМ¶atalo ane Eliodi З¤oniotagodi Jesus Cristo,
\v 4 iniotagodeeЙЎМ¶atalo leeЙЎМ¶odi me jibodicaЙЎМ¶atibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji anodaaЙЎМ¶eni manakatoni Jesus Cristo, codaa anodaaЙЎМ¶eni memaani inatawece loiigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 5 JaЙЎМ¶anakatoni Jesus Cristo codaa adinemaanitiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi manibeoonitegetiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica laЙЎМ¶ajegitedaЙЎМ¶agi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yotetetedaЙЎМ¶adomi digoida ditibigimedi. JaЙЎМ¶ajipaatatiwaji moditece niЙЎМ¶ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yotetetedaЙЎМ¶adomi niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶ajipaatalo niЙЎМ¶inoa notaЙЎМ¶a anewi, notaЙЎМ¶a anele anoditece Jesus Cristo.
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶inoa notaЙЎМ¶a anele jiЙЎМ¶ilaagiteloco inoatawece nipodaЙЎМ¶a codaa joЙЎМ¶owo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me nibinietediniwace oko inoatawece nipodaЙЎМ¶a, mijotaЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶adibinienitetiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo noko maleekoka ajipaatalo lotaЙЎМ¶a anele, codaa ewi mowooЙЎМ¶oti AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji midioka limedi meote aneletoЙЎМ¶odomi.
\v 7 Epafras jiЙЎМ¶ijaa ane ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶axinitecetiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶axa meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi. Codaa Epafras ЙЎМ¶odokaaЙЎМ¶edi ЙЎМ¶odemaanigi, ane yakadi me jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a, ЙЎМ¶obakawa moko liotagi Cristo, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me ЙЎМ¶adaxawanitiwaji.
\v 8 Codaa jiЙЎМ¶iniaa Epafras natematitoЙЎМ¶owa niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶igotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meo meliodi memaani eledi ЙЎМ¶onioxoadipi.
\p 
\v 9 LeeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶obodigitibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a jibodicaЙЎМ¶a, idiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me jipokaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi akaamitiwaji. JipokaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote me yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji Liwigo ЙЎМ¶adixakedi codaa me yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶adowoogo aneotibige mepaanaЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶oti niЙЎМ¶ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yemaa.
\v 10 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa nigakatitiwaji madiniwaxinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atiti mawii ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me eni, codaa mocaЙЎМ¶anitalo, codaa akati mawiite inoatawece anele, codaa mepaanaЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶oti AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 11 Codaa jipokaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji initawece loniciwaЙЎМ¶a ane nelegi, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a akatitiwaji me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateenitedice inoatawece ЙЎМ¶adawikodico, codaa maniniitibecetiwaji.
\v 12 Eleditace jipokaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a akatitiwaji maniotagodeetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji З¤odiodi, aneote me jakataЙЎМ¶a me jibaЙЎМ¶atege niЙЎМ¶ica ane yotetetema loiigi digoida ditibigimedi aneite inoatawece ane datale.
\p 
\v 13 З¤odoЙЎМ¶atedice mejonaЙЎМ¶ateloco loniciwaЙЎМ¶a nexocaЙЎМ¶a, codaa eote Lionigi lemaanigi me iiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\v 14 IniaaЙЎМ¶iniwa Lionigi yeleotedoЙЎМ¶odomi, codaa me ЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶atedice me idejonaЙЎМ¶a nexocaЙЎМ¶a. Codaa leeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo aneote, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\s1 Aniniwa icoa Jesus, codaa niЙЎМ¶ica baaneЙЎМ¶eote
\p 
\v 15 Me jinataЙЎМ¶a Cristo micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a jinataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶icoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane diЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me nadi. Liciagi niЙЎМ¶icoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Cristo jiЙЎМ¶ijaa liidaЙЎМ¶a Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. IniaaЙЎМ¶iniwa naЙЎМ¶axatedeloco inoatawece ane loenataka AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 16 LeeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ibake Cristo meote inoatawece aninoa, digoida ditibigimedi, codaa me digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, niЙЎМ¶inoa ane jakataЙЎМ¶a me jinataЙЎМ¶a, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa ane daЙЎМ¶a jakataЙЎМ¶ateda me jinataЙЎМ¶a. JiЙЎМ¶iniaaЙЎМ¶eote inoatawece niwicidi ane iiЙЎМ¶e eletidi niwicidi, niЙЎМ¶inoa lacilodi niЙЎМ¶inoa niwicidi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa niiЙЎМ¶enatagododi, inoa anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi codaa anida loniciwaЙЎМ¶a. Cristo eote inoatawece ane niwicidi. Inoatawece eote eotedibige me iiЙЎМ¶e.
\v 17 AkaaЙЎМ¶iniwa Cristo niЙЎМ¶ijo maleediЙЎМ¶icoateda niЙЎМ¶inoa aninoa, codaa leeЙЎМ¶odi loniciwaЙЎМ¶a, odaa jiЙЎМ¶inoa inoatawece ane loenataka codaa niЙЎМ¶ina noko oniditecibeci iteloco codaa ilaЙЎМ¶ateloco aneyate.
\v 18 Loiigi Cristo liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶odolaadi. Odaa Cristo jiЙЎМ¶iniaa lacilo ane iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶idi nolaadi. JiЙЎМ¶iniaaЙЎМ¶iniwa aneote me yewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi nolaadi, igaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶iniaaЙЎМ¶iniwa liidaЙЎМ¶a me Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, NiЙЎМ¶ijoa ane yeleo, pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yewikatiditace. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi caticedi inoatawece aninoa.
\v 19 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ane Eliodi Cristo, ninitedibece leeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo me liciagi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 20 Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote lowoogotetece miniaa ibake me nopilaЙЎМ¶aditace miniwataЙЎМ¶a inoatawece digawinitelogo ane jinataЙЎМ¶a codaa me oko, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo Cristo aneote. LeeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo me nadooЙЎМ¶odi lawodi madataЙЎМ¶a nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ilakidetacediwage inoatawece ane jinataЙЎМ¶a digoida ditibigimedi, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa ane jinataЙЎМ¶a digoina iiЙЎМ¶o.
\p 
\v 21 NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji leegitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji motonitedice. Codaa akaami lakapetedipi leeЙЎМ¶otedi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶adowooko ane beyagi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶adoenataka ane beyagi anawiite.
\v 22 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide, leeЙЎМ¶odi Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote me ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, odaa ja yeleo, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja ЙЎМ¶adatecoЙЎМ¶oteenitacetiwaji miniwataЙЎМ¶a, eotedibige me ЙЎМ¶adadeegitedicogitiwaji lodoe, makaami oko ane yapidi, anepaa iomaЙЎМ¶aditedice, me daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica laagedi.
\v 23 Pida leeditibigetiwaji me idapaЙЎМ¶a diiticogi me iwaЙЎМ¶ati liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otigi miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa matitetitiwaji me daЙЎМ¶a amiЙЎМ¶iticoace, codaa me daЙЎМ¶a ikanitiwaji manibeoonitege niЙЎМ¶icoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneetedoЙЎМ¶owa niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a niwakatee niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele anajipaatalotiwaji. EmeЙЎМ¶ee Paulo, ja jao me ee niotagi me jatematitedibece nibodicetedi anele, baanaЙЎМ¶a oilaagaЙЎМ¶aditedeloco moyatematitedibece inatawece iiЙЎМ¶o.
\s1 Ica Paulo libakedi me yaxawa loiigi Cristo
\p 
\v 24 NiЙЎМ¶ina natigide eliodi me idinitibeci me jawikode leeЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶adaxawanitiwaji. NiЙЎМ¶inoa lawikodico yolaadi, leeditibige me jixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedijo, nigepaaЙЎМ¶icota me ixomaЙЎМ¶atedice inoatawece yawikodico ane nikatedici Cristo me jixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedijo. Jawikodetema loiigi Cristo ane micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a lolaadi.
\v 25 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote me ee liotagi loiigi Cristo. Najigotediwa ibakedi me jao aneletaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji. Ibakedi me jeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece inoatawece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 26 NiЙЎМ¶inoa ane doЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi ijotawece oko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja ikeetediogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iomaЙЎМ¶aditedicoace me nepilidi.
\v 27 Lowoogo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ikeetediogi loiigi niЙЎМ¶ica ane yemaa meote. Ikeetediogi niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me ibinie inoatawece ane latopaco noiika. Odaa ja ikee Cristo miniwa catiwedi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me inibeoonaЙЎМ¶atege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶odiweniЙЎМ¶ide anigida noko digoida ditibigimedi miniwataЙЎМ¶a.
\v 28 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mejinaЙЎМ¶atece Cristo minataЙЎМ¶a inatawece oko. JajoinaЙЎМ¶a codaa me jiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a inatawece oko, jibakenaЙЎМ¶a idatawece ЙЎМ¶odixakedi, jaoЙЎМ¶atibige minatawece oko anoyexogotege Cristo aЙЎМ¶ica gaantokaaЙЎМ¶ica libeyacaЙЎМ¶ajegi niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige jadeegaЙЎМ¶a lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 29 Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me idinoniciwaЙЎМ¶aditeloco ibakedi, codaa joletibige me jibotege ane lakakeЙЎМ¶egi ibakedi. Odaa jakadi me jaote inoatawece ibaketedi leeЙЎМ¶odi yoniciwaЙЎМ¶a Cristo ane najigotediwa, eotedibige me jigodi ibakedi.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Enice jemaa mowooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji meliodi me idinoniciwaЙЎМ¶adi me ЙЎМ¶adaxawani, codaa me jaxawa ЙЎМ¶onioxoadipi ane niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a LaodicГ©ia, codaa minatawece eledi ЙЎМ¶onioxoadipi ane diЙЎМ¶icata me etidadi.
\v 2 Jemaa mabo laaleЙЎМ¶ena, codaa jemaa me ilaЙЎМ¶atiwage igaataЙЎМ¶a dinemaatiwage. Eleditace jemaa moyakadi moyowooЙЎМ¶odi mida aneetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo aneotetema, ajemaa daЙЎМ¶a nawienatakanaЙЎМ¶a, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a eneЙЎМ¶egi oyowooЙЎМ¶odi Cristo, NiЙЎМ¶ijoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nikee.
\v 3 Cristo liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina nakabakenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶adi ane yomoke epoagi, igaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶iniaa ikee niЙЎМ¶icoa niliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶icoa ane diЙЎМ¶icoateda monadi niЙЎМ¶ina oko. NiЙЎМ¶idiwa niliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi idatawece niЙЎМ¶ica lixakedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa me lowooЙЎМ¶otakaneЙЎМ¶egi ane yajigote oko.
\p 
\v 4 Jao ЙЎМ¶adeemiditiwaji amanagawini aЙЎМ¶ica ane ЙЎМ¶adinaaleni, aneetece niwitakeco, ibake niЙЎМ¶inoa notaЙЎМ¶a libinienaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 5 IgaataЙЎМ¶a idaaЙЎМ¶ida me leegitibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji, jeemitetece meite ee makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji, eliodi me idinitibeci me jibodicetibigaЙЎМ¶aji me ЙЎМ¶adilakiitiwagetiwaji, idokidata aneni, codaa me atitetiniwace, idioka limedi manakatoni Cristo.
\s1 AnodaaЙЎМ¶ee ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me ЙЎМ¶odilaЙЎМ¶atege Cristo
\p 
\v 6 LeeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodaaЙЎМ¶ee mabaatege Jesus Cristo me З¤aniotagodi, odaa oleetibige midioka limedi me ЙЎМ¶adexocitege.
\v 7 MacataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ana enanigije me ili leeЙЎМ¶otedi litotitedi me ideite catinedi iiЙЎМ¶o, odaa oleetibige midapaЙЎМ¶a diiticogi me ЙЎМ¶adexocitege Cristo, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiliiteloco ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi. Eledi ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina modabiteЙЎМ¶etini diimigi ditibigimedi lipodaЙЎМ¶aladi ane datiteti, joaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ele me enitiwaji me ЙЎМ¶adexocitege Cristo ane liciaceekawa niЙЎМ¶ina diimigi lipodaЙЎМ¶aladi, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a atitetitiwaji codaa midioka limedi manakatoni, anetiЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶axinitece. Odaa idioka limedi maniotagodeetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 8 Adinowetitiwaji adiЙЎМ¶ica aneo makaami nioЙЎМ¶ododi leeЙЎМ¶otedi liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco ane deЙЎМ¶ewiteda, nowooko ane diЙЎМ¶icata jaoЙЎМ¶ate, ane ninaaletiniwace oko. OdiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece inokinoateda epaa lakataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, lixaketedi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, ane daЙЎМ¶a icoЙЎМ¶otedigi miniwataЙЎМ¶a Cristo.
\v 9 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Cristo liciagi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, aЙЎМ¶ica ane diniwokotetece, codaa niЙЎМ¶ijo malee yewiЙЎМ¶a digoina iiЙЎМ¶o me liciagi oko.
\v 10 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji aЙЎМ¶ica anopootibige catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali codaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane aniaditibige, leeЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶adexocitege Cristo, ane lacilo inoatawece niwicidi ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a, codaa minoatawece anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi.
\p 
\v 11 LeeЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶adexocitege Cristo, odaa micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶akagiti ЙЎМ¶adolaadi mijotaЙЎМ¶a ane lakatigi jotigide loiigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide aЙЎМ¶alee ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anoyakagidi ЙЎМ¶adolaadi, pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide Cristo baЙЎМ¶a yakagidi niЙЎМ¶ica ane beyagi catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa meote me ЙЎМ¶adiwokoni loniciwaЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi ane idei catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\v 12 Odaa idaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶adinilegenitiwaji, liciagi deЙЎМ¶etiЙЎМ¶adalicitiniwace, deЙЎМ¶etiЙЎМ¶adawanaЙЎМ¶atitege Cristo, odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja ЙЎМ¶adewikitacetiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace Cristo, leeЙЎМ¶odi me iwaЙЎМ¶ati AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meliodi loniciwaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me iwaЙЎМ¶ati me yewikatiditace Jesus.
\p 
\v 13 NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide akaami Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶otedi ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, codaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me diЙЎМ¶icata anenitege loiigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, anidiwa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco miditaЙЎМ¶a. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote Cristo me yewiЙЎМ¶atace, codaa makaamitiwaji. Codaa ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 14 MicataЙЎМ¶a diЙЎМ¶idiwa ЙЎМ¶onaalewe miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, jinaaleweeЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶otedi ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yedia niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶onaalewe, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶onaalewetalo, leeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo ja yedia ЙЎМ¶onaalewe niЙЎМ¶ijo me yeleotedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate.
\v 15 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yeleotedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate, Cristo ja iЙЎМ¶eke niЙЎМ¶ijoa ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a, codaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi (ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi codaa me niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a). Cristo noЙЎМ¶a loniciwaЙЎМ¶a, codaa ikeetediogi inatawece me niЙЎМ¶ijaa anigaanyeЙЎМ¶egi.
\p 
\v 16 Enice jinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a atacolitece niЙЎМ¶ina anodi minoa eletidi ЙЎМ¶oniiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ane leeditibige mejiwaЙЎМ¶atece. Owote niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco midi ica ane daЙЎМ¶akati melici, macipeta, codaa minoa nokododi ane limedi nalokeco, codaa epenai gela, codaa modi minoa nokododi me inipenaЙЎМ¶atini.
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina liwa oko ane jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a mina menagi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ini oko niЙЎМ¶ini mejinataЙЎМ¶a, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane jaoЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a jiwinaЙЎМ¶ata liwa. Cristo jiЙЎМ¶ijoa menagi, odaa aЙЎМ¶alee leeditibige daЙЎМ¶a jotetenaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa nakataЙЎМ¶a laxokodi ane liciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa wa.
\v 18 JiniЙЎМ¶ica mawiitetiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina aneetaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji mabataa, leeЙЎМ¶odi me daЙЎМ¶a iwitece liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi, igaataЙЎМ¶a diniwikodetibece inokina me lodoe oko, codaa doЙЎМ¶etetiogi aanjotedi. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ini oko mee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mepoka ikeeteta niЙЎМ¶ijo oko niЙЎМ¶ica ane leeditibige me jaoЙЎМ¶a. AnaЙЎМ¶axakeneЙЎМ¶egi, pida aЙЎМ¶ica jibaЙЎМ¶ata, codaa lowooko liciaco lowooko niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida aneetege niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o.
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶ini oko aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a yexogotege Cristo ane ЙЎМ¶odacilo. Cristo eote inatawece lolaadi, ane loiigi, me idapaЙЎМ¶a diiticogi me ili ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me liciagi. Odaa idatawece ЙЎМ¶odilaЙЎМ¶atiwage leeЙЎМ¶odi loniciwaЙЎМ¶a Cristo, micataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odolaadi mowidi laЙЎМ¶aagetedi, pida oniditeci, leeЙЎМ¶otedi ЙЎМ¶odiniocidi inaaЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odomolokenali.
\s1 З¤odeleo pida ja ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶atace miniwataЙЎМ¶a Cristo
\p 
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ademaЙЎМ¶awa Cristo. Odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica anenitege liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa lakataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko. Enige, igaamee ina me ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane beyagi lakataЙЎМ¶a digoina iiЙЎМ¶o? Igaameetiwaji ina me iwitece icoa lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ina oko?
\v 21 IgaataЙЎМ¶a modi, вЂњJinaЙЎМ¶abaata niЙЎМ¶idi!вЂќ, migetaЙЎМ¶a ina modi, вЂњJineЙЎМ¶elici niЙЎМ¶ida niweenigi!вЂќ, вЂњJiniЙЎМ¶itineЙЎМ¶eni niЙЎМ¶idi!вЂќ
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ida nakatigi inoka eetece niЙЎМ¶ina anicota me ma, micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina niweenigi. Enice jinaЙЎМ¶a iwitece niЙЎМ¶inoa nakataЙЎМ¶a oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ane icoЙЎМ¶otedigi minoataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi.
\v 23 Ewi niЙЎМ¶inoa nakataЙЎМ¶a me latopiwatigi daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, igaataЙЎМ¶a odiiЙЎМ¶enataka anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida odoЙЎМ¶etetiogi aanjotedi, codaa odiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me idiniwikodenaЙЎМ¶atibece, pida onowo me diniwikodetibigiwaji, codaa ЙЎМ¶oniiЙЎМ¶etoЙЎМ¶owa me jiloikatitaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odoolatedi. Pida niЙЎМ¶idiwa nakataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶etiЙЎМ¶odaxawa me jakataЙЎМ¶a me jajacaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ani ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena anabeyaceЙЎМ¶e ane yemaatibece meo ane beyagi.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 LeeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yewikatiditace Cristo, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee micataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adewikatititacetiwaji ЙЎМ¶adawanaЙЎМ¶atitetege Cristo. Odaa ele midioka limedi moleetibigetiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica ane idei ditibigimedi, aneite Cristo moiweniЙЎМ¶ide, nicote liwai libaaЙЎМ¶adi Eliodi.
\v 2 Idioka limedi mowoo codaa memaanitibige niЙЎМ¶ica ane idei ditibigimedi, idiЙЎМ¶ida jineЙЎМ¶emaanitibige niЙЎМ¶inoa aninoa niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o.
\v 3 IgaataЙЎМ¶a micataЙЎМ¶a daantaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adelewitiwaji (odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica anenitege niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide anenitiwaji), pida ja ЙЎМ¶adewikitiwaji awanitege Cristo me yewiЙЎМ¶a. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anaЙЎМ¶a ikee niЙЎМ¶ica gela ЙЎМ¶adewiЙЎМ¶atiwaji.
\v 4 LeeЙЎМ¶odi Cristo naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace, odaa nige dinikeetace, oko eledi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote me ЙЎМ¶odeloЙЎМ¶o codaa ЙЎМ¶odiweniЙЎМ¶ide ЙЎМ¶odawanaЙЎМ¶aditetege Cristo.
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide anejinaЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a icaaЙЎМ¶ica gela ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a
\p 
\v 5 JinaЙЎМ¶awii ane beyagi ane yemaa ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali, pida awii micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko baanaЙЎМ¶a yeleo aЙЎМ¶alee yakadi meo ane beyagi. Enice jinaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adoomatewa ane daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adodawa. JinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a emaanitibige niЙЎМ¶ina ane napioi, jinaЙЎМ¶awii, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owoo niЙЎМ¶ina ane napioi ane ilidaЙЎМ¶aditigi ЙЎМ¶adoolatedi. JineЙЎМ¶emaanitibige midioka limedi meliodi niЙЎМ¶ina anakati, igaataЙЎМ¶a nigidaaЙЎМ¶eni ja daЙЎМ¶axa maweniЙЎМ¶ideni niЙЎМ¶ica anakamaЙЎМ¶a emaani, odaa aЙЎМ¶alee oЙЎМ¶eetetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 6 JinaЙЎМ¶awiitetiwaji niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yelatetema codaa eliodi me iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane deЙЎМ¶eyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda.
\v 7 NiЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji jaЙЎМ¶awiite niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi, codaa inoka awiite niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali ane yemaa.
\p 
\v 8 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide ele mikani mawiite niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi, jinaЙЎМ¶a eliЙЎМ¶idee, codaa jinoЙЎМ¶oteteni ЙЎМ¶adelaЙЎМ¶a catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali, codaa jinaЙЎМ¶awii ane beyagitema eledi oko. JinaЙЎМ¶abeyacaЙЎМ¶ati ЙЎМ¶agegi motaЙЎМ¶ani, codaa jineЙЎМ¶eni inoa notaЙЎМ¶a ane napioi.
\v 9 Codaa jinaЙЎМ¶adininaalenitiwaji, igaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶ikani niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide aneni codaa jiЙЎМ¶ikani niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶adakataЙЎМ¶a laxokodi.
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji jiЙЎМ¶ida gela aneni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa, anidioka limedi me ili, eote micota me ЙЎМ¶adiciagi, digo miniwataЙЎМ¶a, codaa eote mepaanaЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶oti AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 11 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me daЙЎМ¶alee ibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ina oko mige judeu, oЙЎМ¶oa domige ajudeu; domige yakagidi lolaadi, oЙЎМ¶oa domige ayakagidi lolaadi; migetaЙЎМ¶a iomiЙЎМ¶igi; domige nialigipijegi; domige niotagi, oЙЎМ¶oa domige aniotagi. Pida okotawece iniokiniwateda Cristo mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate, codaa ina me yewiЙЎМ¶a catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\p 
\v 12 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶adiolaatedicetiwaji, ЙЎМ¶adiomaЙЎМ¶atitedice makaami loiigi, codaa me ЙЎМ¶ademaani. Enice adiniwikodenitiwaji, oleetibige makaami eletema eledi oko, adiniwikodenitibece lodoe eledi oko, codaa ocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni eledi oko, codaa adinatiitalo niЙЎМ¶inoa anicinoa.
\v 13 Adinatiita eledi oko. Nigicatibece ina ЙЎМ¶adileenigitema eledi oko, dioki ixomaЙЎМ¶ateenitice anowotaЙЎМ¶adomi ane beyagi. MijoataЙЎМ¶a Cristo me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice ЙЎМ¶adoenataka ane beyagi, awii digo mijoataЙЎМ¶a anee.
\v 14 Odaa ane daЙЎМ¶axa me leeditibige madinemaanitiwaji, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adilakiitiwage, codaa me ЙЎМ¶adeЙЎМ¶enakitiwaji.
\p 
\v 15 Jemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji midioka limedi meote mele ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali, amanagawini owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji mawii niЙЎМ¶ica anewi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adixipenitedicoace eote makaami lapo oko ane ilaЙЎМ¶atiwage, codaa eotedibige mele ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali. Codaa midioka limedi maniotagodeetalo.
\v 16 Oleetibige mele mowookonitiwaji codaa midioka limedi me nalaЙЎМ¶atibigaЙЎМ¶aji niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco anoyalaЙЎМ¶atalo Cristo, codaa mele me iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶ani, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina me aladeeni eledi oko, abakeni initawece ЙЎМ¶adixakedi ane yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Codaa agaani Enaco ane diniditelogo lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa eletidi Enaco, codaa agaani noЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶eco ane ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶axinitece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo. AgaanaЙЎМ¶anitibigimece З¤oniotagodi, codaa oleetibige midioka limedi maniotagodeetalo manitawece ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena.
\p 
\v 17 Enice okanicodaaЙЎМ¶icoateda ane ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶a, codaa mokanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica anawii, oleetibige manelecaЙЎМ¶ateeni LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi З¤oniotagodi Jesus. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina maniotagodeetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, З¤odiodi, abakeni LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi Jesus.
\s1 Anodaa leeditibige me eni madiniwaxinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atiti lodoe eledi oko leeЙЎМ¶odi naЙЎМ¶a gela ЙЎМ¶adewiЙЎМ¶a
\p 
\v 18 Akaamitiwaji, iwaalepodi, iwaЙЎМ¶ati ЙЎМ¶adodawadi, igaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶idaa leeditibige me eni leeЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶adexocitege З¤oniotagodi.
\v 19 Akaamitiwaji, ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, emaani niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶adodawadi, codaa jinaЙЎМ¶akaami aojokomatadipi.
\p 
\v 20 Akaamitiwaji anakaami nionigipi, oleetibige midioka limedi me iwaЙЎМ¶ati ЙЎМ¶adiododipi, igaataЙЎМ¶a З¤oniotagodi jiЙЎМ¶idaa yemaa me eni, akaamitiwaji ane iwaЙЎМ¶ati З¤oniotagodi.
\v 21 Akaamitiwaji anakaami eniododipi, jinaЙЎМ¶awii ЙЎМ¶adionigipi me neliЙЎМ¶ideeЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi anemiitiogi moxoki, adaЙЎМ¶awiitibige midioka limedi magecaЙЎМ¶alodipi.
\p 
\v 22 Akaamitiwaji anakaami niotagipi, ele midioka limedi me iwaЙЎМ¶ati ane ЙЎМ¶aniotagodi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o. Odaa jinaЙЎМ¶a iwaЙЎМ¶ati inokina niЙЎМ¶ina mida me ЙЎМ¶adiwini doЙЎМ¶oleetibige mocaЙЎМ¶anita, ane lakatigi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida aneetege niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o. Pida oleetibige me iwaЙЎМ¶ati ЙЎМ¶aniotagododipi inoatawece anoiiЙЎМ¶etedaЙЎМ¶awa, mele ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena, leeЙЎМ¶odi me eemiteetigilo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 23 NiЙЎМ¶ina mawiitiwaji okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica nibakedi, adinoniciwaЙЎМ¶ati mawii nibakedi anele, micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a З¤oniotagodi iiЙЎМ¶etedaЙЎМ¶awa mawii niЙЎМ¶ida nibakedi, jiniЙЎМ¶idoka ixomitiwece ЙЎМ¶adacilo meledi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni mawii.
\v 24 IgaataЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji З¤oniotagodi micota me yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ica laЙЎМ¶ajegitedaЙЎМ¶agitiwaji digoida ditibigimedi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a Cristo jiЙЎМ¶iniaa ane З¤oniotagodi ane jibaaЙЎМ¶atema.
\v 25 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina anidioka limedi meo ane beyagi aibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi anini niЙЎМ¶ini oko, pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigote loojedi ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi aneo. IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji idokidata anigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko micataЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶oko diniciamico. AЙЎМ¶ica ini aneote me iomiЙЎМ¶igi idatawece ЙЎМ¶odiciaceeketediwage niЙЎМ¶ina me leeditibige me ЙЎМ¶odiloikatidi.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Akaamitiwaji aninoa ЙЎМ¶aotaka, adowetitelogo ЙЎМ¶aotaka, ajicitiogi niЙЎМ¶ica ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a modibatege. Analakitibige maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iniwa З¤aniotagodi digoida ditibigimedi.
\s1 Paulo ladeenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco
\p 
\v 2 Oleetibige midioka limedi motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, jiniЙЎМ¶ikani motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni. Atacolitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶oti nige yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa anipokitalo, odaa aniotagodeetalo.
\v 3 Codaa ipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jakataЙЎМ¶a mejinaЙЎМ¶atece Cristo, codaa me jikeenaЙЎМ¶a anewi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda Cristo. Ite ee niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi leeЙЎМ¶odi mejitece Cristo.
\v 4 Codaa leeditibige mejitece Cristo amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a eliodi oko oyowooЙЎМ¶odi. Codaa ipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji minatawece iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a moyowooЙЎМ¶odi yotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina mejitece Cristo.
\p 
\v 5 Abakeni ЙЎМ¶adixakedi niЙЎМ¶ina midatecibece madinadeegitege niЙЎМ¶ina oko analeedoЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda З¤oniotagodi. NiЙЎМ¶ina midatecibece makati maxawani, odaa ikeenitiogi mida anenitege Cristo.
\v 6 Abakeni ЙЎМ¶adixaketedi amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idioka limedi mele motaЙЎМ¶ani, enitece notaЙЎМ¶a anida ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶oti ane alitigi ЙЎМ¶agegi magiti okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica oko.
\s1 Owidijedi lotaЙЎМ¶a Paulo me yecoaditibige Colosseensitedi
\p 
\v 7 JiiЙЎМ¶e TГ­quico migo yatematitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji inoatawece ane jixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice. TГ­quico ЙЎМ¶onioxoa aneliodi me jemaanaЙЎМ¶a, codaa eledi liotagi З¤oniotagodi anidioka limedi meo ane iiЙЎМ¶ete З¤oniotagodi, codaa midioka limedi me ЙЎМ¶odaxawatece libaketedi З¤oniotagodi.
\v 8 Jimonya migo makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji, jaotibige mica ibodigitibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji, codaa jaotibige me ЙЎМ¶adaxawanitiwaji me ili ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egitema З¤oniotagodi.
\v 9 З¤onioxoa OnГ©simo jiiЙЎМ¶e me lixigaЙЎМ¶awa TГ­quico. OnГ©simo ЙЎМ¶onioxoa aneliodi me jemaanaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me jakataЙЎМ¶a me jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a. Eledi ida anenitegetiwaji. NiЙЎМ¶idi iniwata ЙЎМ¶onioxoadipi oyatematitaЙЎМ¶awa anodaaЙЎМ¶eeta digoina anejo.
\p 
\v 10 З¤onioxoa Aristarco anini meetaЙЎМ¶a digoina niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi, yecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji, codaa ЙЎМ¶onioxoa Marcos eledi yecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji. Marcos letexegi BarnabГ©. JaЙЎМ¶abaatege yajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi ane jidi mele mabaatege Marcos, nigicotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji.
\v 11 JosuГ©, aneledi liboonaЙЎМ¶adi me Justo, eledi yecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji. NiЙЎМ¶idiwa iniwatadiЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi З¤oniotagodi, niЙЎМ¶idi jiЙЎМ¶idiokidi me judeutedi ane ibakawepodi. Eliodi metidaxawatece ibakedi, mejitece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yemaa me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko.
\p 
\v 12 З¤onioxoa Epafras yecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji. Epafros elatibige ЙЎМ¶anigotaЙЎМ¶a, inaaЙЎМ¶ina liotagi Jesus Cristo, codaa midioka limedi me dinoniciwaЙЎМ¶adi me yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi akaamitiwaji. Dipokotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji matiteteloco ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa mele mowooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco aneetece З¤oniotagodi, codaa dipokotalo midioka limedi mowooЙЎМ¶oti codaa mawiite inoatawece ane iiЙЎМ¶etedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 13 EmeЙЎМ¶ee jinadi codaa jakadi meji Epafras meliodi me diba me ЙЎМ¶adaxawanitiwaji, codaa me yaxawa ЙЎМ¶onioxoadipi ane niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotadi LaodicГ©ia aniaa HierГЎpolis.
\v 14 З¤onioxoa Lucas, dotowegi aneliodi me jemaanaЙЎМ¶a, iniaa Demas eledi oyecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶aji.
\p 
\v 15 Adecoateenitece niЙЎМ¶ina anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi З¤oniotagodi ane niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a LaodicГ©ia, codaa adecoateenitece ЙЎМ¶onioxoa NГ­nfas, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ica lapo anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi Cristo ane dinatecoЙЎМ¶otee liЙЎМ¶eladi NГ­nfas.
\v 16 Nigagoti malomeЙЎМ¶eniteloco naЙЎМ¶adi iwakate, odaa iwakateeniticogi naЙЎМ¶adi yotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi miditaЙЎМ¶a lapo anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi З¤oniotagodi digoida nigotaЙЎМ¶a LaodicГ©ia, codaa mawii maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyalomeЙЎМ¶eteloco naЙЎМ¶adi iwakate. Codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a alomeЙЎМ¶eniteloco notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi ane icoЙЎМ¶otigi LaodicГ©ia.
\v 17 Enita ЙЎМ¶onioxoa Arquipo, вЂњDigawini! Oleetibige magoti ЙЎМ¶abakedi anabaatege, leeЙЎМ¶odi mida anenitege З¤oniotagodi!вЂќ
\p 
\v 18 Ee Paulo, emeЙЎМ¶ee jidi iboonaЙЎМ¶adi me idecoaditibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji. JinaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adaagititiwaji me ee niwilogojegi. Jemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji midioka limedi meletedaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. (AmГ©m).
